oracle.spatial.rdf.client.jena

Class OracleUserRuleBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • oracle.spatial.rdf.client.jena.OracleUserRuleBase

  • public class OracleUserRuleBase
extends java.lang.Object
    This class implements a rulebase that corresponds to the Oracle Database 11g Release rulebase design. Note that it is possible for a rulebase to exist without being readable (or writable) for the user that created the Oracle connection. The name of the user-defined rulebase MUST not be the following: RDF, RDFS, RDFS++, OWLPRIME, OWLSIF.

      • getAllRules

        public java.util.Iterator getAllRules()
                               throws java.sql.SQLException
        Returns all rules in this rulebase. The iterator returned consists of elements of type OracleUserRule. The Filter field in Oracle user-defined rules is simply ignored. Only the first triple pattern in the rule head is processed.
